     H            Y.
     F** UEXR10C ********************************************
     F*  PROGRAM: EXSUB - UPDATE MASTER LABEL#              *
     F*  WRITTEN: JW (SRA) 2021.04.13                       *
     F*-----------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UEXR10C'
     F*                    PARM           $SHID  10
     F*                    PARM           $MAST  18
     F*  IN  $SHID  10A  SHID
     F*  IN  $MAST  18A  MASTER LABEL#
     F******************************************************
     FAB#EP67 UF  E           K        DISK
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $SHID  10
     C                     PARM           $MAST  18
      *===================================================
      *           MAIN ROUTINE
      *===================================================
      *
     C           $SHID     SETLLAB#EP67
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C           $SHID     READEAB#EP67                  98
     C   98                LEAVE
      *
     C           E7LSQN    IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVEL$MAST     E7LSQN
     C                     UPDATAB#EP671
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
